@API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5090

### Get channels list (paginated, with optional search)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/analytics/channels?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Get channels list with search (e.g. search for "110kV")
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/analytics/channels?search=110kV&page=1&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Detect spikes with HOURLY granularity for ALL channels (ChannelId omitted)
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/analytics/detect-spikes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "granularity": "Hour",
  "confidence": 95,
  "windowSize": 30,
  "startDate": "2026-06-20T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-06-25T00:00:00Z"
}

###

### Detect spikes with DAILY granularity for a SPECIFIC channel
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/analytics/detect-spikes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channelId": 1234,
  "granularity": "Day",
  "confidence": 98,
  "windowSize": 7,
  "startDate": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-06-25T00:00:00Z"
}

###

### Detect spikes with CUSTOM 15-minute granularity for a SPECIFIC channel
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/analytics/detect-spikes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channelId": 5678,
  "granularity": "Custom",
  "customMinutes": 15,
  "confidence": 95,
  "windowSize": 60,
  "startDate": "2026-06-24T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-06-25T00:00:00Z"
}
